OL,5,G1600 The World at War
OL,6,     FPincers: Laurence Olivier provides
OL,7,     Fthe narration to this World War II
OL,8,     Fretrospective. Hear how 1944 saw
OL,9,     Fthe steady disintegration of the
OL,10,     FGerman war machine, as the Allies
OL,11,     Fadvanced.
OL,12,G1700 Secret Nazi Bases
OL,13,     FA Secret Canal: With Nazi
OL,14,     FGermany's rise to power, a
OL,15,     Flong-abandoned canal project in
OL,16,     FEast Prussia is resurrected, but
OL,17,     Fthe true purpose of this massive
OL,18,     Fwaterway comes into question.
