OL,10,     FEdward VIII.
OL,11,G1900 Dom Chinea's Cornish Workshop
OL,12,     FDom builds a drift car with
OL,13,     Fengineer Sam Lovegrove. At home,
OL,14,     Fhe gets a digger in to make his
OL,15,     Fnew pond, and he and Sam have a go
OL,16,     Fat gig rowing after fixing the
OL,17,     Fclub trailer in Hayle.
